{"tid":1517743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[聽日無民陣］一齊出港島買嘢？","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T04:58:47.000Z","uid":79965,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69e0cc159162c52d95708b97b00675bd4bc2050d","tid":1517743,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"太好啦！聽日無遊行！<br />\n其實講真呀，和理非呢一刻可能仲驚遊行嘅時候有衝擊，有得揀佢地一定寧願出去購物！<br />\n我個人行街就最鍾意人多，逼下逼下好似年宵咁先有趣。為免聽日條街唔夠人，我希望<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全世界叫齊你D姨媽姑姐，聽日出港島大shopping！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要說遊行，試著說聽日港島大shopping</span></span><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 就黎開學，聽講金鐘開始沿線到西營盤都好多嘢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49726bfceb99ae390b651158e15bc817ec65c618","tid":1517743,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:19:28.000Z","msg":"快D share 俾你嘅親朋好友啦！"},{"pid":"9b3c02242f45a1404fafc3984a6e4f4e915f53ee","tid":1517743,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"43311cbc41215d4c3979c69b426731768e974b4c","tid":1517743,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"有無人聽日想陪我出去買嘢，唔想自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead68ce32f8895335fc36f9b2b42ffaa1c1e6e72","tid":1517743,"uid":276429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:20:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cdf54304f6a215f60a369a9c8c5bb1a1b7451ac9","tid":1517743,"uid":79965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"救救寂寞的連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653e19618448be71a0456d1f5f5a95c089579e55","tid":1517743,"uid":140538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re